org.ctoolkit.restapi.client.provider

Interface AuthKeyProvider


  • public interface AuthKeyProvider
    The provider to provide implementation specific mechanism to retrieve authentication key for API authentication (from file, encrypted datastore etc).

    The implementation is optional and once configured will take a precedence. See ApiCredential.ApiCredential(String) for more info how prefix is being used.

    Author:
    Aurel Medvegy
